    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Solitaire with a Bloody Twist</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stack villager cards in order to collect them to their safe spots. Beware, however, as a secret is hiding among them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032430/extras/a61c7ee37d097acc0947820c88a4a8c4.poster.avif?t=1755275495\" width=800 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032430/extras/a61c7ee37d097acc0947820c88a4a8c4.webm?t=1755275495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032430/extras/a61c7ee37d097acc0947820c88a4a8c4.mp4?t=1755275495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>Vampire</strong> will transform poor villagers into vampires, trying to block their escape routes. Do not fret, though! The <strong>Priest</strong> is here to heal vampires and transform them into villagers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Adapt your strategy, find the balance and master the endless dance between Fangs &amp; Faith!</p>",
